	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我呀，<delay20 /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />现在正在模拟一下，<delay8 />
