<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />建设一个国家吗？”<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多美好啊！<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />原来你说的白马王子<20_2 arg="3" />不是比喻，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />指的是真正的王子啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这已经不能算是模拟了……<delay20 />
是不是应该叫幻想才对？<anim id="Eh" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />梦想当然是非常重要的。<delay20 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但如果沉浸于捉摸不到的梦境中，<delay20 />
