	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呜！<20_2 arg="4" /><pageBreak />讨厌～！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />你这个人，<delay20 />
