<anim id="OhGeez" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />太没意思了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有问题要问<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果给你机会变成<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" />一整天，<anim id="Nodding" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />成为我之后，<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你想做些什么？<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="0" /><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊！<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<anim id="FaintSmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
