回答一下这个问题吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这又是什么？<20_2 arg="1" /><delay20 />
