<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我想想，<delay20 /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果是我的话<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那肯定还是要穿上可爱的衣服，<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
