<20_3 arg="8" /><delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。<20_2 arg="6" /><20_3 arg="4" /></message>
	<message label="103_a" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="player" targetSpec="" />当然是做偶像！</message>
	<message label="103_b" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">做个笑星吧……</message>
	<message label="103_c" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />保持自己的特色就好了！</message>
	<message label="104" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真的～？<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你们怎么都这么想做偶像的啦！<anim id="Smiling" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那，<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />干脆我们组一个团体吧？<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />三人行！偶像组合！<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="105" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">“如果是<tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /><tag a="110" b="13" />”<20_2 arg="1" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />的前提呢？<delay8 />
