	<message label="106" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Shocked" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这样啊！<20_2 arg="2" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把我的<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />可爱<delay20 />
