<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />给组合起来的话<tag a="110" b="0" />！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那肯定会出现一个<anim id="WrySmile" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
