<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" />模仿一下这个风格呢……<anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="107" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" />像你这样<20_2 arg="1" />积极主动的人，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大概做什么都能有模有样吧。<anim id="FaintSmile" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="108" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="TakenAback" target="actor" targetSpec="" />保持<20_2 arg="2" /><delay20 />自己的特色？！<10_4 />
<anim id="Frantic" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那是什么？<delay20 />听起来好帅～！<anim id="Eh" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是呀～！<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我才不想要做别人！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因为我就是我，<anim id="Dance" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />
