<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在<delay20 />感觉已经超～级明白了！<anim id="ColdChill" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="109" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我还被骗着<anim id="EmotEnd" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><20_2 arg="1" />认真地回答了一下，<delay8 />
