	<message label="202" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">咦？<20_2 arg="3" /><delay20 />怎么一回事？<delay20 /><anim id="Smiling" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />发生了什么吗？<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="203" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只是在练习<delay8 />
偶像的毕业表演而已啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过总感觉，<delay8 /><20_2 arg="4" />最后好像很难完美收场，<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就好像<delay8 />缺了一些
什么东西呀～<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="mainNpc" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="204" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我觉得在你<20_2 arg="3" />练习自己的毕业表演之前，<delay20 />
